data.description: Pfabulous in Pflugerville! This immaculately maintained home boasts a floorplan and design that you will want to call home. 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths with a primary ensuite that includes a garden tub and a separate shower. The dedicated office is perfectly placed at the front of the home. Both formal and kitchen dining is just what you need for hosting friends and family and the extra natural light pouring into the kitchen from the skylight ads an ambiance for all to enjoy. Newer kitchen appliances and counter space galore perfectly finishes off the heart of the home in the kitchen area. You will enjoy the large family room with a beautiful gas fireplace. The roof was replaced in 2021 and the HVAC was replaced in 2020.
